responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "1043576C45A97415969B498C21B3F407", "The dry goods here have turned rancid since the transports have been getting ransacked by the vagrants. You can\'t blame \'em, really, since they aren\'t the kind to sit around and be swindled. A shame though, you\'d think we could get a decent set of oils.")
